# Cloudflare Pages SPA fallback. Wildcard form is required: an exact
# rule like `/auth/callback /index.html 200` is silently overridden by
# Pages's directory-normalisation 308 (path → `/`), which strips the
# `/auth/callback` from the OIDC redirect — observed in prod 2026-05-09.
# `/*` is the standard SPA pattern and applies before normalisation.    # L2_隔離
/*   /index.html   200
